OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FFrance have won the Six Nations after
OL,7,Fbeating England 48-46 in Paris.
OL,9,FIt comes after Scotland's hopes of
OL,10,Ftheir first title in 27 years were
OL,11,Fdashed when they list their final
OL,12,Fmatch to Ireland by 43 points to 21.
OL,14,FEngland cast off the shackles to
OL,15,Fdeliver their best performance of the
OL,16,FGuinness Six Nations but it was not
OL,17,Fenough to stop Thomas Ramos from
OL,18,Flanding a last-gasp penalty to ignite
OL,19,FFrench title celebrations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
