PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FTommy Freeman produced a brilliant
OL,7,Ffinish with three minutes left of an
OL,8,Fexhilarating clash in Paris to propel
OL,9,FEngland in front, but Ramos found the
OL,10,Fposts from long-range in the final act
OL,11,Fof the Championship to clinch a 48-46
OL,12,Fvictory.
OL,14,FSteve Borthwick's side were
OL,15,Ftransformed from the side that
OL,16,Fcollapsed to three consecutive
OL,17,Fdefeats, running in seven tries as
OL,18,Ftheir attack finally fired with the
OL,19,Foutstanding Ollie Chessum crossing
OL,20,Ftwice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FIt was also the night their pack
OL,7,Fflexed their muscles for the first
OL,8,Ftime in the tournament by submitting
OL,9,FFrance up front, inspired by Chessum,
OL,10,Fthe relentless Ben Earl and props
OL,11,FEllis Genge and Joe Heyes.
OL,13,FBut they were hurt by their eighth
OL,14,Fyellow card of the tournament shown to
OL,15,FGenge and the exquisite finishing of
OL,16,FLouis Bielle-Biarrey, who touched down
OL,17,Ffour times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
