PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FIt was the type of all-action display
OL,7,FBorthwick needed to convince the Rugby
OL,8,FFootball Union he should continue as
OL,9,Fhead coach just a week after England
OL,10,Ffell to a historic first defeat by
OL,11,FItaly.
OL,13,FA gripping spectacle was only marred
OL,14,Fby the decision to allow France to
OL,15,Fplay in light blue anniversary kit to
OL,16,Fmark 120 years of 'Le Crunch',
OL,17,Fresulting in a colour clash with
OL,18,FEngland's white jerseys.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
