PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FIreland's pulsating victory over
OL,7,FScotland that launched 'Super
OL,8,FSaturday' presented France with the
OL,9,Ftarget of winning in Paris to retain
OL,10,Ftheir crown ` a prospect that was
OL,11,Fanything but assured after a
OL,12,Fbreathless first-half.
OL,14,FIt looked ominous for England when
OL,15,FBielle-Biarrey finished the first of
OL,16,Fhis two tries after collecting Ramos'
OL,17,Fkick after just six minutes, but
OL,18,Funlike in previous rounds they
OL,19,Fresponded to the adversity by showing
OL,20,Ftheir teeth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
