PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FAttacking down both touchlines, they
OL,7,Fquickly went over with Elliot Daly
OL,8,Fpulling the trigger for Tom Roebuck in
OL,9,Fa deserved try given the ambition of
OL,10,Ftheir play.
OL,12,FIt sent the tone for the rest of the
OL,13,Fhalf with the rivals regularly
OL,14,Fexchanging tries, with Bielle-Biarrey
OL,15,Fthe main threat for the hosts through
OL,16,Fhis ability to capitalise on any
OL,17,Fhesitation in defence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
