PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FMatthieu Jalibert's kick allowed him
OL,7,Fto score his second, but England hit
OL,8,Fstraight back when Cadan Murley
OL,9,Ftouched down a Ben Spencer grubber
OL,10,Fthat slipped through the hands of Theo
OL,11,FAttissogbe.
OL,13,FIn a rare display of emotion,
OL,14,FBorthwick slammed his hand down on his
OL,15,Fdesk in celebration of the try.
OL,17,FFor the first time in the tournament,
OL,18,FEngland's pack began to snarl with the
OL,19,Fmaul emerging as a potent weapon with
OL,20,Fthe second of two powerful drives
OL,21,Fending when Chessum dived over.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
