OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FAnd then their forwards combined in
OL,7,Fattack with Chessum sending Alex Coles
OL,8,Fover with Spencer also involved as
OL,9,Fspace down the blindside was exploited
OL,10,Fbrilliantly.
