PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FThere was so much to admire about
OL,7,FEngland's performance but their 10-
OL,8,Fpoint lead faded in first-half added
OL,9,Ftime when referee Nika Amashukeli
OL,10,Fdecided Genge had collapsed a maul,
OL,11,Fshowing him a yellow card and awarding
OL,12,Fa penalty try.
OL,14,FIt then evaporated completely as
OL,15,FBielle-Biarrey completed his hat-trick
OL,16,Fwhen France's attack clicked soon
OL,17,Fafter the interval before Attissogbe
OL,18,Fstruck on the other wing after
OL,19,Fgathering a long pass from Antoine
OL,20,FDupont.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
