PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773626592
OL,3,CFrance win Six Nations 2026 after
OL,4,Cclose victory over England
OL,6,FChessum produced a brilliant read to
OL,7,Fgallop home for an intercept try and
OL,8,Fthen a build up of pressure created
OL,9,Fspace for Marcus Smith to cross on his
OL,10,F50th cap.
OL,12,FEngland were stung by a breakaway try
OL,13,Ffor Bielle-Biarrey but when France
OL,14,Fprop Demba Bamba was sin-binned they
OL,15,Fpounced for the sixth time through
OL,16,FFreeman, only for Ramos to kick the
OL,17,Ftitle-winning penalty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
